&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/r/error-in-match/"&gt;error-in-match&lt;/a&gt; — value not found in lookup&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/r/error-in-which/"&gt;error-in-which&lt;/a&gt; — logical condition error&lt;/li&gt;
